sequenceDiagram
    actor Cliente
    participant UI as IncidentReportScreen\nmobile/lib/incident_report_screen.dart
    participant API as incidents.py -> incident_controller.py
    participant S as incident_service.py\nreport_incident()
    participant R as incident_repository.py\nIncidentRepository
    participant T1 as Tabla vehiculo
    participant T2 as Tabla estado_servicio
    participant T3 as Tabla incidente
    participant T4 as Tabla evidencia
    participant T5 as Tabla historial

    Cliente->>UI: 1. Selecciona vehiculo y agrega evidencia
    UI->>API: 1.1 POST /api/v1/incidentes/reportar + Bearer JWT
    API->>API: 1.2 require_mobile_cliente valida token y rol
    API->>S: 1.3 report_incident(payload, cliente_id)
    S->>R: 1.4 get_vehicle_for_client(placa, cliente_id)
    R->>T1: 1.5 SELECT vehiculo del cliente
    S->>R: 1.6 get_or_create_service_state('pendiente')
    R->>T2: 1.7 SELECT/INSERT estado_servicio
    S->>S: 1.8 process_incident_payload_for_ai(...)
    S->>R: 1.9 create_incident(...)
    R->>T3: 2.0 INSERT incidente
    S->>R: 2.1 create_evidence(imagen/texto)
    R->>T4: 2.2 INSERT evidencia
    S->>R: 2.3 create_history(eventos iniciales)
    R->>T5: 2.4 INSERT historial
    S-->>API: 2.5 Incidente registrado y procesamiento iniciado
    API-->>UI: 2.6 201 Created
    UI-->>Cliente: 2.7 Mostrar confirmacion